content.title: Episode 10
content.shortDescription: Uncle Otis takes a trip to a lost gold mine in 'Pups Save a Jungle Miner', then in 'Pups Save Uncle Otis From His Cabin', smart tech ends up trapping Uncle Otis and Mr. Wingnut indoors! (S7, ep 13)

content.title: Episode 9
content.shortDescription: Pups Save the Pupmobiles: Mayor Goodway gives the team the key to the city. When Sid Swashbuckle and his trusty pirate pup Arrby swipe it, Ryder and the pups team up to solve the mystery. (S7, ep 12)

content.title: Episode 8
content.shortDescription: Pups Save a Hum-Dino: Mayor Humdinger takes his Kitties to the Dino Wilds for some Dino acting lessons, but instead finds himself on top of a runaway Brachiosaurus. (S7, ep 8)
